CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 24, 1955, pg. A15 reads: "Headed For Santa...is one-year-old Cheryl Ann Harris, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Charles (Teenie) Harris, of Pittsburgh, their first little girl. Cheryl, a veritable young dynamo of action, is better known as "Tiny" and celebrates her birthday Dec. 27. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Cheryl "Tiny" Harris wearing duck patterned dress, standing in front of record player in home of Charles "Teenie" Harris, 7604 Mulford Street, Homewood
